## Constraints

1. Output ONLY the README.md contents — no commentary, no code fences around the output
2. Extract site variables by finding ALL `var(--name, fallback)` patterns in the CSS
3. Be descriptive but concise in the "What It Controls" column
4. In "Extending in Code", provide examples that make sense for THIS component type
5. If the component has `applyTagSelectors: true` in its config, include the Tag Selectors section
6. Keep the tone professional and developer-focused
7. Use exact markdown formatting as shown in the template
8. Ensure all tables are properly formatted with alignment
9. The component name in the title should be the PascalCase componentName, not kebab-case

